company.name: Wequips
company.description:
Wequips is focusing on providing solutions in the construction-, maritime- and offshore industry. Wequips offers equipment/tools; materials and services to contractors; port authorities and government agencies. 
Wequips always strives to offer tailor-made solutions for each customer. Our broad range of solutions and services are categorized in five different product groups: (i) Drilling, Screening & Trenching; (ii) Piling (impact & micro) & Vibrating; (iii) Cutting & Demolition; (iv) Draining, Pumping, Dredging & Oil Spill Recovery; and (v) Foundation Software & Rendering.

Wequips is conveniently located in Panama City, and has the possibility to give customers service in Central and South America; both in Spanish as English.

http://www.wequips.com/
